        "setup": "In the [SingleStore Cloud Portal](https://portal.singlestore.com/), select your organization, then go to **Configuration → API keys → Active Keys → Create API key**. Give the key a name and expiration date, then create it. The portal shows the key only once, so copy and store it securely.",
