        "label": "SingleStore database username and password",
        "setup": "Create a database user for your SingleStore deployment. For Helios, first add a database user via [Manage Database Users](https://docs.singlestore.com/cloud/user-and-workspace-administration/manage-database-users/), then use that `username` and `password` for Data API Basic auth.",
        "acquisition": "manual"
